title: Celebrity Family Feud, Jill Scott, Chuck Woolery, Washington NFL and more.

description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! Lady Shirley, Lady Carla and The Champ are all here to entertain you. Let's just say The CLO has sedation and lack of performance issues that he helps people with today. Jilly from Philly got the clapback. Celebrity Family Feud got folks runnin' ten miles! What does 45, Dr. Fauci and Chuck Woolery have in common? Huge changes are happening for our Washington NFL franchise. Another weekend of gun violence in Chicago claimed lives and injured many. Houston Rockets star Paul Westbrook tested positive for COVID-19. Today in Closing Remarks, Uncle Steve has analogy that is an absolute gem and so much more!
